#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="sn22.12"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn22.12:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 22 "
msgstr "Linked Discourses 22 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn22.12:0.2"
msgid "2. Aniccavagga "
msgstr "2. Impermanence "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn22.12:0.3"
msgid "12. Aniccasutta "
msgstr "12. Impermanence "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p><span class="evam">
#. REF: sc1
msgctxt "sn22.12:1.1"
msgid "Evaṃ me sutaṃ—"
msgstr "So I have heard. "

#. HTML: </span>
msgctxt "sn22.12:1.2"
msgid "sāvatthiyaṃ. "
msgstr "At Sāvatthī. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn22.12:1.3"
msgid "Tatra kho … pe … "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn22.12:1.4"
msgid "“rūpaṃ, bhikkhave, aniccaṃ, vedanā aniccā, saññā aniccā, saṅkhārā aniccā, viññāṇaṃ aniccaṃ. "
msgstr "“Mendicants, form, feeling, perception, choices, and consciousness are impermanent. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn22.12:1.5"
msgid "Evaṃ passaṃ, bhikkhave, sutavā ariyasāvako rūpasmimpi nibbindati, vedanāyapi nibbindati, saññāyapi nibbindati, saṅkhāresupi nibbindati, viññāṇasmimpi nibbindati. "
msgstr "Seeing this, a learned noble disciple grows disillusioned with form, feeling, perception, choices, and consciousness. "

msgctxt "sn22.12:1.6"
msgid "Nibbindaṃ virajjati; virāgā vimuccati. Vimuttasmiṃ vimuttamiti ñāṇaṃ hoti. "
msgstr "Being disillusioned, desire fades away. When desire fades away they’re freed. When they’re freed, they know they’re freed. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn22.12:1.7"
msgid "‘Khīṇā jāti, vusitaṃ brahmacariyaṃ, kataṃ karaṇīyaṃ, nāparaṃ itthattāyā’ti pajānātī”ti. "
msgstr "They understand: ‘Rebirth is ended, the spiritual journey has been completed, what had to be done has been done, there is no return to any state of existence.’” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn22.12:1.8"
msgid "Paṭhamaṃ. "
msgstr ""

#. HTML: </p></article></section></body></html>
